## Animations

```css
:root {
  /* Transition Durations */
  --duration-75: 75ms;
  --duration-100: 100ms;
  --duration-150: 150ms;
  --duration-200: 200ms;
  --duration-300: 300ms;
  --duration-500: 500ms;
  --duration-700: 700ms;
  --duration-1000: 1000ms;
  
  /* Transition Timing Functions */
  --ease-linear: linear;
  --ease-in: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 1, 1);
  --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);
  --ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

/* Animation Classes */
.fade-in {
  animation: fadeIn var(--duration-300) var(--ease-in-out);
}

.slide-up {
  animation: slideUp var(--duration-500) var(--ease-out);
}

.pulse {
  animation: pulse var(--duration-1000) var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
}

/* Keyframes */
@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes slideUp {
  from { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; }
  to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.7; }
}
```

